{"tid":2369251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"浸聯會牧函轟大搜捕 籲為真理長期爭戰","createTime":"2021-01-17T03:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T04:09:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"82a63e8f88432beda6c47cb50cfab37e3130d102","tid":2369251,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/O77XHG6JFRC2JP65PX43MMQS3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FO77XHG6JFRC2JP65PX43MMQS3U%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=3ec24a09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FO77XHG6JFRC2JP65PX43MMQS3U%2F&h=31d4032d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/O77XHG6JFRC2JP65PX43MMQS3U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n浸聯會牧函轟大搜捕 籲為真理長期爭戰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uadcntj8eRErcEGv66u7CxmnbEA=/1123x1829/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PG5XC5UMEVGRLEJ6B73DOQRMIQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fuadcntj8eRErcEGv66u7CxmnbEA%3D%2F1123x1829%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPG5XC5UMEVGRLEJ6B73DOQRMIQ.gif&h=4bd2e042&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年年中刮起的寒流，一直沒停下來，我城一片肅殺。55名泛民因參與立法會初選被指控顛覆國家政權，三位關注社會的牧者在基督教媒體時代論壇發表牧函回應，勉勵弟兄姊妹繼續追求公義和真理。其中香港浸信會聯會會長羅慶才牧師說：「真理與虛假之戰，是長期的爭戰。我們必須要忍耐，惟有忍耐到底，才能得見其成就。」<br />\n<br />\n羅慶才在牧函中指出，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n袁天佑：國安法如刀架市民頸<br />\n<br />\n他相信，此刻大家都帶着焦慮和不安，「靜心」等待案件走完整個司法程序，而不論最終判決如何，香港整體的社會關係及政治生態，已經起了不可逆轉的變化。但他引述希伯來書勉勵大家：「你們不可丟棄勇敢的心，存這樣的心必得大賞賜。你們必須忍耐，使你們行完了上帝的旨意，就可以得着所應許的。」<br />\n<br />\n另一位牧師袁天佑形容，國安法是架在市民頸項上的刀，任由當權者解讀，壓制異見人士。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蒲錦昌：考驗和困厄是生命常態<br />\n<br />\n袁天佑形容，刻下香港人心惶惶，有逃亡，有移民，有人無奈不能離港，也有人選擇留港，堅持到底。他說：「不論離開與否，大家都熱愛香港，希望香港能有民主和自由。香港教會的前途，取決於我們能否與香港人同行。相信上帝真光的人，更要在香港人中散發光明。」<br />\n<br />\n蒲錦昌牧師則說：「香港如烏雲密佈，大風暴快要來臨的一刻：更可怖的恐怕還在後頭。」。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uT2OpSWoIqtyFt2fIZz7TSSITc4=/1182x898/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MU6DSB5PWJHC5DB7B4UWBTM2ZQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuT2OpSWoIqtyFt2fIZz7TSSITc4%3D%2F1182x898%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMU6DSB5PWJHC5DB7B4UWBTM2ZQ.gif&h=87aeef5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IzkBk8c9wJ875BfZrFVkp20AD2E=/1182x857/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WG3YDMDZVRB7XNGQ4UY3K3CHOE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIzkBk8c9wJ875BfZrFVkp20AD2E%3D%2F1182x857%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWG3YDMDZVRB7XNGQ4UY3K3CHOE.gif&h=49a3f0bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26ca9199ba3314b1637f131fb1701da49b0e45f1","tid":2369251,"uid":161711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:42:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e009c4eb1ac335485cd2787a5a4dc969336251cf","tid":2369251,"uid":381265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T04:09:48.000Z","msg":"push"}]}